Class Glsl300ShaderGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jme3.shader.ShaderGenerator
      • com.jme3.shader.Glsl100ShaderGenerator
        • com.jme3.shader.Glsl150ShaderGenerator
          • com.jme3.shader.Glsl300ShaderGenerator

  • public class Glsl300ShaderGenerator
extends Glsl150ShaderGenerator
    This shader Generator can generate Vertex and Fragment shaders from ShaderNodes for GLESSL 3.0 Nowdays it's just a subclass of Glsl150ShaderGenerator overriding the version string because GLSL 1.5 is mostly compatible with GLESSL 3.0
